info.name: aspose-cells-python
info.summary: Aspose.Cells for Python via .Net is a scalable and feature-rich API to process Excel spreadsheets using Python. Developers can format worksheets, rows, columns or cells, create manipulate chart and pivot tables, render worksheets, charts and specific data ranges to PDF or images, add calculate Excel’s builtin and custom formulas - all without any dependency on Microsoft Office or Excel application.
